{
    "name": "Undigested Swarm",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Whereas individual undigested are more of a nuisance than a threat to adventurers, a swarm of such creatures can be dangerous to even experienced adventurers. An undigested swarm comprises hundreds of individual undigested. Driven by insatiable hunger, they fall upon and consume any living creatures crossing their path, surrounding the unfortunate victims and drenching them in acidic slime, digesting their still-living prey even before the screaming ends."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>This brown-and-yellow sludge appears to be made of multiple smaller globules churning in a disgusting communal mass.</i>",
