                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A target that takes swarm damage from an undigested swarm is covered in acidic slime and must succeed at a DC 16 Reflex save or take 2d6 points of acid damage for 1d4 rounds at the start of its turn. An affected creature can make a new save as a full-round action. Washing off the acid grants a +4 bonus on this save. The save DC is Constitution-based."
